{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"772c0adb94","title":"中共中央关于十月社会主义革命五十周年纪念办法的通知","origin":"根据《中共中央文件汇编，1966.5-1968.5 [内部参考]》，1968年5月出版，编印者不明","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"93fef9c9ab","index":0,"year":1967,"month":10,"day":25,"articleId":"772c0adb94"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"70a3c7b93d","type":"title","text":"中共中央关于十月社会主义革命五十周年纪念办法的通知","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"772c0adb94"},{"id":"4dcdd1e880","type":"paragraph","text":"今年十一月七日是伟大十月社会主义革命五十周年。中央决定纪念办法如下：","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"772c0adb94"},{"id":"2d81ead3a6","type":"paragraph","text":"一、《人民日报》《红旗》杂志和《解放军报》联名发表纪念社论。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"772c0adb94"},{"id":"47627ebe49","type":"paragraph","text":"二、在首都举行纪念大会，由林彪同志作报告。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"772c0adb94"},{"id":"ee1b859be8","type":"paragraph","text":"三、上海、沈阳、天津、武汉、西安、成都、广州等大城市也举行纪念会。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"772c0adb94"},{"id":"7e667df8cb","type":"paragraph","text":"四、纪念会一般不邀请外宾。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"772c0adb94"},{"id":"cae7313d4c","type":"paragraph","text":"五、在节日前后放映《列宁在十月》等电影。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"772c0adb94"},{"id":"0ff7dc43b2","type":"paragraph","text":" 中共中央一九六七年十月二十五日","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"772c0adb94"}],"page":{"id":"27e688a063","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"772c0adb94","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}